# Common Interview Mistakes

❌ HTTP remembers previous requests.

✅ HTTP is Stateless.

---

❌ GET is used for Login.

✅ POST is generally used because credentials are sent in the request body.

---

❌ PUT and PATCH are identical.

✅ PUT replaces the entire resource.

PATCH updates only selected fields.

---

❌ 401 and 403 are the same.

✅ 401 → Authentication required.

✅ 403 → Authenticated but not authorized.

